data.description: Beautiful 3BD, 2BA home nestled in serene Belair. The stylish kitchen includes new appliances, granite countertops, backsplash, and all new cabinets. Stay comfortable with the new HVAC system, insulation, & hot water heater for energy efficiency. Outside you will find an oasis with new privacy fence, extended pool apron, & a vinyl liner pool complete with a new pool filter. It is perfect for relaxation and family fun. New flooring in bedrooms add a fresh feel to the private spaces. Call today for your tour!
